1. Get the Full Path of the executable of the application
2. vi ~/Desktop/IntelliJ.desktop
3. Enter content as :

#!/usr/bin/env xdg-open
[Desktop Entry]
Version=1.0
Type=Application
Terminal=false
Exec=/snap/intellij-idea-community/72/bin/idea.sh
Name=IntelliJ
Comment=Intelli J IDEA Community
Icon=/snap/intellij-idea-community/72/bin/idea.png

4. Go to Desktop and change the permission of the file to executable.
5. Double Click. If warning given for untrusted souce click on Trust and Launch.
6. Done !
